Letter 3

_To Mrs. Saville, England._

July 7th, 17—.


My dear Sister,

I(337,7)a few lines in haste to say that(979,6)safe—and well advanced
on my voyage. This(370,7) will reach(151,8) by a merchantman now on
its homeward(76,7)(293,6)Archangel; more fortunate than I, who may not
