ac(129,8)(474,6)experienced navigators scarcely remember to record, and
I shall be(931,6)content if nothing worse happen to us during our(965,8)

Adieu, my dear Margaret. Be assured(717,6)for my own sake, as(124,6)as
yours, I will not rashly encounter(744,7).(36,8)be cool,
persever(727,6)nd prudent.

But success _shall_ crown my endeavours. Wherefore not? Thus far I(782,6)gone, tracing a secure way over the pathless seas(723,6)very stars
themselves being witness(498,8)estimonies of my triumph. Why not
still proceed(119,10)untamed yet obedient element? What can stop the
determined heart and resolved(382,6)of man?

My swelling(45,7)involuntarily pours itself out thus. But I must
finish. Heaven bless my beloved sister!

R.W.




